Refactors ProgramsPage component for better readability
Extracts program content logic into separate component Replaces useEffect with a cleaner function to get title Adds Suspense component with loading indicator for lazy loading
Relates to JIRA-456

Fixes type definition and imports in ProgramInformation
Adds missing type definition for onValueChange function Corrects TabsContent import to resolve dependency issue
Adds size prop to BackToTop button and updates job opening display to use h3 for role
Reorders import statements in Toggle component for consistency
Updates tailwind-merge to version 3.2.0 and modifies clean script in package.json

Refactors API response handling and context usage
Updates API endpoints to use NextResponse for JSON handling Refactors context parameter usage for improved type safety Adds category information in staff member responses
Adds new creative writing pieces to student work showcase and updates main images for existing entries
Adds dark mode support to Testimonial component styling

Reorders imports in NavBar component
Repositions DockNavigation import for consistency. Moves ThemeToggle component to correct place in the navigation menu.
Removes TestimonialCards and TestimonialSection components; updates TestimonialCard styling for consistency

Improves StudentWorkCard layout and styling
Updates image container for better aspect ratio and clipping Simplifies alt text for images Enhances text gradient with dark mode support

Updates StaffCards component for dark mode support
Reorders imports and removes unused import. Improves icon color handling to support dark mode. Fixes group-hover class removal for header text.
Adds dark mode support to ProgramCards component styling
Removes border styling from showcase item images for improved visual consistency
Improves FAQ section styling for better dark mode support

Adds dark mode styling to About Us page
Updates various elements on the About Us page to include dark mode styles, enhancing user experience in dark mode environments.
Updates package-lock.json and package.json for dependency version upgrades and adds rebuild script

Refactors parameter extraction in GET handler
Simplifies parameter destructuring in GET handler Improves readability by removing unnecessary variable assignment

Enhances UI consistency and accessibility
Incorporates `ResponsiveLogo` across various pages for branding consistency. Refines text components for improved readability and accessibility. Adjusts layout structures to ensure responsive design compatibility. Removes redundant code and unused elements for cleaner implementation. Fixes minor visual inconsistencies in components like `StudentWorkCard`.
No related issue mentioned.
Adds "Provide Us Feedback" option to contact navigation

Updates contact page content and heading
Revises the page heading to "Contact Us" for clarity. Enhances the description text to provide detailed information about outreach opportunities, including collaboration and feedback.
Improves user engagement by offering a welcoming and informative tone.
Adds ProvideFeedbackPage component with feedback form and instructional content

Enhances form functionality and UX
Adds required attribute to key input fields for validation in ApplicationForm. Introduces file upload support for resume and cover letter with drag-and-drop UI. Refactors FeedbackForm to use state management for dynamic input handling and submission. Improves accessibility and styling consistency across forms.
Updates background color in FadedImage component for consistency

Refactors imports and updates styles for consistency
Reorganizes imports to reflect new directory structure and ensures consistency across components. Enhances visual hierarchy by adding dark mode support to headings. Fixes CSS variable inconsistencies and resolves minor typo in variable names. Removes unused components and consolidates redundant ones for better maintainability.

Updates program image lists for consistency
Revises image paths across chess, basketball, and soccer programs to ensure consistency and include additional images. Removes duplicates and outdated entries while adding new ones to enhance the visual content.
Improves program presentation and organization.

Adds feedback form component
Introduces a new feedback form with fields for name, email, and message. Includes basic validation to ensure all fields are required.

Refactors FAQs into categorized structure
Groups frequently asked questions into categories for better organization and readability. Improves clarity by aligning questions and answers with specific themes such as program structure, registration, and safety measures.

Removes unused components and redundant code
Deletes obsolete components from the codebase, including a page header and testimonial grid, to reduce clutter and improve maintainability.
No functional changes introduced.

Refactors TestimonialCard component for reusability
Replaces hardcoded testimonial content with dynamic props for flexibility. Simplifies layout and styling while maintaining functionality. Enhances maintainability and scalability of the component.

Updates layout and improves job application UX
Revises heading structure for better accessibility and design. Enhances job application section with updated messaging and a dedicated "Contact Us to Apply" button. Removes redundant "View all openings" button for cleaner UI.

Refines FAQ and Testimonials page designs
Enhances FAQ page layout with improved sectioning and styling. Adds a responsive logo and an image for visual appeal. Refactors FAQ rendering logic for better structure and readability.
Updates Testimonials page to use a dedicated TestimonialCard component. Improves text and image layout for a more polished user experience.

Refines application and request pages layout and content
Updates layouts for consistency with unified styling Enhances textual content to improve user engagement Replaces placeholder text with meaningful descriptions Removes unused icons and address details for simplicity Introduces a FadedImage component for visual appeal

Refactors UI components and improves accessibility
Updates heading hierarchy for semantic correctness Improves layout consistency across components Enhances image alt text for better accessibility Removes redundant utility imports and optimizes styling
No issue linked

Standardizes heading hierarchy and improves accessibility
Replaces `<h2>` tags with `<h3>` across various pages to ensure proper heading hierarchy. Improves semantics by converting text elements to `<code>` where appropriate. Adds new components like `FadedImage` and updates forms for better usability. Refines layout and content structure for improved readability and accessibility.
Fixes #456
